# Battery
To make Ideal Battery

What id Ideal Battery

Ideal Battery
Energy input = Storage Energy(99%)+Heat loss(1%)
Energy output = Released Energy(93-96%)+Heat loss(7-4%)
Energy output = Direct Current
Its direct current can be converted and inducted to alternating current by an inverter.
The battery is readily rechargable.
It can be charged by any type of electricity.
It is biosafety.
Fire hazard probability shall be < 14%.
